data.description: This stunning home features a modern interior with 4 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and an open living/dining area. The kitchen boasts all-white cabinets, contemporary countertops, a custom island, and decorative lighting. The main bedroom includes a large bathroom and a his and hers closet space. Enhancements include high-quality tile floors, 8 ft doorways, extremely spacious backyard. Additional perks include plantation shutters, a large epoxy-coated garage, and easy access to top schools. A rare opportunity to enjoy luxury and convenience in a prime location.
